242:- **rivetkit (TypeScript)** (`rivetkit-typescript/packages/rivetkit/`) — TypeScript-friendly API. Calls into rivetkit-core via NAPI for lifecycle logic. Owns workflow engine, agent-os, and client library. Zod validation for user-provided schemas runs here.
